## id: supermicro-bmc-panel
## name: Supermicro BMC Login Panel - Detect
## author: hack007x
## severity: info
## tags: panel,supermicro,bmc,discovery
## description: Supermicro BMC login panel was detected.
## affects: x11ssv-m4f
## reference: https://www.supermicro.com/en
